#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Tummy Time Safari*"
msgstr "Isikhathi Sokuphuma Sesafari"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Time for an adventure - right on the floor! 🌱"
msgstr "Isikhathi sezinselelo"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "✅ Lay a soft blanket on the floor and gently place your baby on their tummy. Put a few colourful toys or soft books just out of reach, and see your baby reach for them. "
msgstr "Ndlala ingubo entofontofo phansi ubeke ingane yakho kahle ngesisu. Beka amathoyizi ayimibalabala noma incwadi ethambile lapho ingezukwazi ukufinyelela kuzo, ubuke ingane ifinyelela kuzo "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👀 Talk, sing, or lie down face-to-face to keep them engaged."
msgstr "Khuluma, ucule, noma ulale ngaphambi kwayo nibukane ukuze umenze azizwe ebambisene nawe."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🧸 Make it playful - wiggle a toy or a plastic bottle with some rice like an animal exploring the jungle! “Look, here comes a lion!”"
msgstr "Yenza kube umdlalo - nyakazisa ithoyizi noma ibhodlela leplastikhi elinerayisi njengesilwane sihlola ihlathi! \" Bukani sekuqhamuka ibhubesi\"!"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Tummy time is essential for your baby’s physical development and builds the strength they’ll need to crawl and sit ⭐"
msgstr "Isikhathi sokuphuma sibalulekile ukuthuthukisa ukukhula komzimba wengane yakho futhi kwakha amandla abawadingayo ukuthi bakhase nokuhlala"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Face to Face Fun*"
msgstr "Ukujabulisana ubuso nobuso"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Babies love looking at faces - especially yours! 😃"
msgstr "Izingane ziyathanda ukubuka ubuso - kakhulu obakho"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👑 Sit comfortably and hold your baby so you’re face-to-face. Make funny faces, raise your eyebrows, puff your cheeks, and talk or sing gently."
msgstr "Hlala unethezeke uphathe ingane yakho ngendlela yokuthi niyabukana. Yenza ubuso obuhlekisayo, unyuse amashiya, phaphatha izidlathi zakho futhi ukhulume noma ucule mnene."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🚩 Watch as your baby starts to copy you! Peek-a-boo and big smiles are great ways to bond."
msgstr "Bukela lapho ingane yakho iqala ukukulingisela! Umdlalo ka Mbophe phoyisa nokumamatheka indlela enhle yokuxhumana."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "This activity helps your baby develop emotional connection, eye contact, and early social skills - all while having fun together 🎉"
msgstr "Lomsebenzi usiza ukuthi ingane yakho ukuthuthukisa ukuxhumana ngokozwelo, ukuxhumana ngokubukana, amakhono okuqala ukuxhumana - konke lokhu ngesikhathi sokujabula ndawonye"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Sing & Sway*"
msgstr "Cula futhi uzungeze"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🎵 Hold your baby close and gently sway together to the rhythm of a soft song. You can hum or sing a lullaby as you move, making eye contact and smiling as you go."
msgstr "Bamba ingane yakho uzungeze nayo nilandela ingoma edlalela phansi. Ungacula ingoma yokulala njengoba unyakaza, nibukane nimamatheke ulokhu uqhubeka."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔄 Try singing the same song each day - it creates a lovely routine and helps your baby recognise familiar sounds over time."
msgstr "Zama ukucula ingoma eyodwa zonke izinsuku- lokhu kwakha isijwayelo sokuthi ingane yakho ikwazi ukuzwa umsindo ojwayelekile zikhathi zonke."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "The soothing movement helps your baby feel safe and connected, while the sound of your voice supports early language development and emotional bonding 💛"
msgstr "Ukunyakaza ngokumnene kusiza ukuthi ingane yakho izizwe iphephile futhi kunukuxhumana, njengoba izwi lakho kwesekela ukuthuthukiswa kolimi kusenesikhathi nokuxhumana ngokozwelo"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "It’s a simple, calming way to bond and build your baby’s growing brain through rhythm, movement, and love 🌙"
msgstr "Indlela elula, ukuxhumana ngokuzola ukwakha ukukhula komqondo enganeni yakho ngesigqi, umnyakazo nothando"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Toe Tickle Talk*"
msgstr "Inkulumo ngokuqabula unyawo"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Let’s explore toes and fingers with a gentle tickle and some fun words! 👋"
msgstr "Make sihlole ukukitazwa ngokumnene ezinzwaneni nase minweni yezandla namagama amunandi"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "▶️ Start by wiggling your baby’s toes or fingers one at a time while counting them, saying your own silly rhyme, or simply naming the toes and fingers: “Tickle your tiny toe!” or “Hello little thumb!”"
msgstr "Qala ngokunyakazisa izinzwane noma iminwe unyakazisa ngayinye ngesikhathi uzibala, ube uzisholo ingoma yakho ewubuwula, noma usho izinzwane neminwe ngamagama\" Kitaza ucikicane\" noma \"Sawubona sthupha esincane!\""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "This activity strengthens your baby’s awareness of their body and supports early language learning - all while sharing giggles and smiles 🎉"
msgstr "Lo msebenzi uqinisa ukuthi iqaphele umzimba wayo ingane yakho nokweseka ukufunda ulimi masinyane - konke ngesikhathi nabelana ngokuhleka nokumamatheka"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Follow the Sound*"
msgstr "Landela umsindo"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Let’s explore the world of sound! 📻"
msgstr "Make sihlole umhlaba womsindo"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "💡 Find something in your house that makes a gentle sound, like some rice in a packet or a plastic bag. "
msgstr "Thola into enomsindo omnene lapho endlini yakho, njenge rayisi elisephaketheni noma kuplastikhi "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👂 Gently make a sound with the object near your baby’s ear - first on one side, then pause and try the other."
msgstr "Yenza umsindo omnene ngalento oyitholile uwenzele eduzane nendlebe yengane - uqale kolunye uhlangothi, bese uphumula kancane bese uzama eduze kwenye kolunye uhlangothi."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👀 Watch how your baby turns their head to follow the noise. You can even say, “Over here!” as you move the sound."
msgstr "Buka ingane yakho ukuthi iliphendula kanjani ikhanda ilandela umsindo. Ungasho ukuthi \" Ngapha\" ngesikhathi unyakazisa uhambisa umsindo."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "This is a lovely, quiet way to play together - and it helps your baby start to understand how sound connects to movement. It supports their attention and brain development 🌱"
msgstr "Lena iyona ndlela enhle enokuthula yokudlala ndawonye - futhi isiza ingane yakho ukuqala ukuqonda ukuthi umsindo nomnyakazo kuxhumana kanjani. Yesekela ukuqaphela nokukhula komqondo"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Story Cuddles*"
msgstr "Izindaba zokugona"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "It’s never too early to share a story! 📖"
msgstr "Akusheshile ukuxoxa indaba"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👂 Hold your baby close and tell them a simple story – you can tell them about your day or memories from when you were young, or you can make up a short story."
msgstr "Phath uyibambele eduze ingane uyixoxele indaba elula -ngamxoxela ngosuku lwakho noma okukhumbulayo ngezikhathi zakho usemncane noma ungazakhela indaba emfushane."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "💙 Your baby may not understand what you are saying yet, but the sound of your voice, your expressions, and the closeness all help them feel safe and connected."
msgstr "Kungenzeka ingane ingakuqondi okushoyo ngalesosikhathi, kodwa umsindo wephimbo lakho, indlela oyibeka ngayo indaba, ukusondelana konke lokhu kungayisiza izizwe iphephile futhi kunokuxhumana."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👀 If you share a story from a book, you can point to pictures and describe what you see: “Look, a dog! The dog is playing outside.”"
msgstr "Uma umfundela indaba esencwadini, ungakhomba izithombe futhi uchaze okubonayo: \"Buka, inja! Inja idlala ngaphandle.\""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Story telling builds language, imagination, and a love of stories and reading - right from the start. And cuddling up together makes it even more special ✨"
msgstr "Ukuxoxelana izindaba kwakha ulimi, umcabango ukuthanda izindaba nokufunda - ekuqaleni. Nokugonana kwenza kube ngokukhethekile ngokwedlulele"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Name That Sound*"
msgstr "*Qamba lowomsindo"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Make everyday noises into a fun game! 🎵"
msgstr "Yenza umsindo wansuku zonke kube umdlalo omnandi"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔑 Use objects like a crinkly bag, keys, or tapping a cup. Make a sound and then pause."
msgstr "Sebenzisa izinto ezifana nesikhwama esigoqiwe esihlofozelayo, okhiye noma ushaye inkomishi. Yenza umsindo bese uyama kancane."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👂 Say what it is: “Crinkle, crinkle! That’s the bag!” or “Clink clink! That’s the keys!” Watch your baby’s reaction - do they turn toward the sound? Do they smile or blink?"
msgstr "Yisho ukuthi yini\"Hlofo, hlofo! \"Isikhwama lesi\" noma ushayanise! Okhiye labo \"Buka ukuthi ingane yakho izokwenzenjani - ingabe iphendukela ngalapho ekunomsindo khona? Ingabe uyamamatheka noma uyacwayiza?"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "This activity builds your baby’s listening and attention skills while helping them begin to link sounds to the world around them."
msgstr "Lo msebenzi wakha ikhono lokulalela kwengane yakho nokuqaphela okusiza ukuqala ukuxhumanisa umsindo nomhlaba omzungezile."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Even the smallest sounds can open up a big world of discovery! 🌈"
msgstr "Ngisho nomsindo omncane ungavulela amathuba okuthola kumhlaba omkhulu"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Follow the Beat*"
msgstr "Landela isigqi"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🎵 Use your hands to gently clap or pat a simple rhythm on your little one’s legs or arms: “Ta-ta-ta... ta-ta!”"
msgstr "Sebenzisa izandla zakho uzishaye ngokumnene noma umbambathe isigqi esilula emlenzeni noma engalweni yengane yakho: \"Ta-ta-ta... ta-ta\"!"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "😃 Then pause and smile - do they respond? Your little one may wiggle, kick, or if they are a bit older they may even copy the rhythm."
msgstr "Bese uyama kancane umamatheke- ngabe uyaphendula? Ingane yakho inganyakaza, ikhahlele noma uma ekhulile kancane angakopela isigqi leso."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "This playful call-and-response builds listening, rhythm, and connection - just like traditional music has done for generations 💚"
msgstr "Lomdlalo wokuqala - uphendule ufundisa ingane ukulalela, isigqi, nokuxhumana - njengomculo wasemandulo wawenza kwizizukulwane"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Scarf Peekabo*"
msgstr "Ukuzifihla nokubonisa ngesikhafu"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "It’s peekaboo time - with a twist! 🎁"
msgstr "Isikhathi sokuzifihla uziveze - okunomehluko"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔶 Grab a soft scarf or cloth and gently hide your face behind it. "
msgstr "Thatha isikhafu esintofontofo noma indwangu uzifihle ubuso ngayo "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👋 Then slowly pull it away and say, “Peekaboo!” with a big smile."
msgstr "Kancane, kancane uyidonse sakuyivula bese uthi \" Ngiyakubona\" ngokukhulu ukumamatheka."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🧸 Try hiding your baby’s favourite toy or your baby’s feet too. Each reveal is a surprise, sparking joy and curiosity!"
msgstr "Zama ukufihla ithoyizi lengane yakho eliyintandokazi noma izinyawo zengane. Ngakunye kuveze ngokumangazayo, uvuselele injabulo nelukuluku!"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "This playful activity encourages visual tracking, helps build anticipation, and supports early social interaction 👀"
msgstr "Lomdlalo ugqugquzela ukulandela ngamehlo, kusiza ukwakha ukulindela, nokweseka ukuxhumana nomphakathi ngokushesha"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Peekaboo is more than just fun - it teaches your baby that things (and people!) still exist, even when they’re out of sight ✨"
msgstr "Ukucasha nokuvela kungaphezu kwenjabulo - ifundisa ingane yakho ukuthi izinto nabantu kusekhona, noma bengekho ngaphambi kwamehlo ethu"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Adapted from UNICEF Playbox: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=trQ1tFuagzQ"
msgstr "Iguqulwe kusuka kwibhokisi lokudlala lakwa UNICEF: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=trQ1tFuagzQ"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Mirror Moments*"
msgstr "Isikhathi sesibuko"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "It’s time to meet someone special - themselves! 👋"
msgstr "Isikhathi sokuhlangana nomuntu obalulekile - uqobo lwabo"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "😃 Stand in front of a mirror or reflecting window with your little one and watch their reaction. "
msgstr "Ima ngaphambi kwesibuko noma iwindi elicwebezelayo nengane yakho ubuke ukuthi uzokwenzenjani "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👀 You can point to their nose or eyes and name them aloud: “There’s your nose!”"
msgstr "Ungakhomba ikhala noma amehlo akhe uzisho ngamagama azo kakhulu:\"Nali ikhala lakho!\""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🚩 For older babies, encourage them to touch the mirror or make faces. Smile, wave, and copy their movements!"
msgstr "Ezinganeni esezikhulakhulile, bagqugquzele ukuthinta isibuko bese benza ubuso obuhlukahlukene. ukumamatheka, ukuvalelisa bese wena ukopela umnyakazo wabo!"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Mirrors support self-awareness, recognition, and early language development - plus, they’re lots of fun! 💙"
msgstr "Izibuko zisekela ukuziqaphela, ukuqashelwa nokuthuthukisa ukukhula kolimi ngokushesha - futhi lokhu kuyajabulisa"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Texture Treasure Hunt*"
msgstr "Ukufuna Umcebo Wezinto Ezihlukahlukene Ezithintwayo"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Let’s explore the world through touch! 🌱"
msgstr "Make sihlole umhlaba ngokuthinta"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "✅ Collect safe objects with different textures - like a soft sock, a wooden spoon, a smooth ball, or a crinkly wrapper. "
msgstr "Qoqa izinto eziphephile ezingazwakali ngokufana uma uzithinta - njengetshe elithambile, isipuni sepulangwe, ibhola elibushelelezi noma iphepha elihlofozelayo "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👋 Gently guide your baby’s hands over each item and describe them: “Soft,” “Bumpy,” “Cold.”"
msgstr "Hola ingane yakho ngesandla kuzo zonke lezi zinto futhi uzichaze: \"Ithambile,\" \"Imahadla,\" \" Iyabanda.\""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🧸 Encourage older babies to choose what they want to touch. You can even let them sit in or next to a basket with the objects and explore freely."
msgstr "Gqugquzela izingane esezikhulile ukuthi bakhethe ukuthi bafuna ukuntinta ini. Ungabavumela bahlale eduzane nobhasikidi onalezinto bese beyahlola ngokukhululeka."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "This sensory activity helps develop touch, language, and curiosity - and it’s perfect for quiet bonding time ⭐"
msgstr "Lomsebenzi wokuzwa usiza ukuthuthukisa ukuthinta, ulimi nelukuluku - futhi ilungele isikhathi esinokuthula sokuxhumana"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Playtime with Books*"
msgstr "*Isikhathi Sokudlala Ngezincwadi*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Reading to your baby from birth is a beautiful way to bond and support their development - even before they understand the words 📖"
msgstr "Ukufundela ingane kusukela izelwe yindlela enhle yokuxhumana nokusekela ukhula kwabo - nangaphambi kokuthi baqonde amagama"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "⏰ Choose a quiet moment, turn off distractions like TV and phones, and pick a baby-friendly book or even an old magazine or newspaper you have lying around!"
msgstr "Khetha isikhathi esinokuthula, cisha konke okungaphazamisa njenge TV namafoni, bese ukhetha incwadi eyintandokazi yengane yakho noma iphephandaba elikhona ekhaya!"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "💚 Talk about the pictures, make sounds, and repeat simple words. Your baby will love hearing your voice - even if they don’t understand yet."
msgstr "Khulumani ngezithombe, nenze umsindo, futhi niphindaphinde amagama alula. Ingane yakho izothokozela ukuzwa iphimbo lakho - noma bengakaqondi okwamanje."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Follow their lead - if they lose interest, that’s okay. Keep it short and fun! 😃"
msgstr "Landela ukuhola kwabo - uma kwenzeka belahlekelwa umdlandla, kulungile. Kwenze kube kufishane kujabulise"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔄 If possible, start a regular routine to read together when your child isn’t too tired or hungry.\rReading together for a few minutes a day is one of the best ways to help your child learn words and connect with you!"
msgstr "Uma kungenzeka, qala isejwayelo sokufunda ndawonye uma ingane yakho ingakhathele kakhulu noma ingalambile. Ukufunda ndawonye imizuzu embalwa ngosuku indlela enhle yokusiza ingane ukufunda amagama nokuxhumana nawe!"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Act Out Emotions*"
msgstr "Lingisa imizwa"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Let’s have some fun expressing feelings! 😃"
msgstr "Ake sibe nenjabulo ngokuveza imizwa"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👀 Tell your child, “Let’s see what it looks like when I am happy!”. Act out a happy face and name the emotion again. "
msgstr "Tshela ingane yakho, \" Ake sibone kubukeka kanjani uma ngijabule! \"Lingisa ubuso obujabulile uphinde usho umuzwa "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "😔 Then try other emotions, like angry, sad, or surprised. Using a gentle voice, you can explain different reasons why you are feeling that emotion."
msgstr "Bese uzama eminye imizwa, njengokuthukuthela, ukudangala noma ukumangala. Ungakhuluma ngezwi eliphansi uchaza izizathu ezehlukene ukuthi kungani uzizwa ngaloluhlobo."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "This isn’t just a game - it’s a chance for your child to learn how to recognize emotions in others 💚 "
msgstr "Akusiwo umdlalo nje lona - ithuba lokuthi ingane yakho ifunde ukuqaphela imizwa kwabanye abantu "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "By understanding facial expressions, they’ll strengthen their connections with others and develop empathy 💛"
msgstr "Ngokuqonda inkulumo yobuso, kuzoqinisa ukuxhumana nabanye babe nozwelo"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "So, get ready to act out some emotions and enjoy this special play activity together! 🌈"
msgstr "Zilungiselele ukulingisa eminye imizwa futhi ukuthokozele ukudlala okukhethekile ndawonye"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Adapted from I am Safe, Loved, and Learning by Save the Children"
msgstr "Iguqulwe ku Ngiphephile, Ngithandiwe nesifundo sakwa Save the Children"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Animal Sounds & Moves*"
msgstr "Imisindo yezilwane neminyakazo"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Let’s roar like a lion or flap like a bird! ⭐"
msgstr "Ake sibhonge njengebhubesi noma sishaye amaphiko njengenyoni"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "📖 Show your baby a soft animal toy or picture and say its name: “This is a lion - roooar!” "
msgstr "Khombisa ingane yakho ithoyizi lesilwanyana esithambile noma isithombe bese usisho igama laso. \"Leli ibhubesi - bhonga\" "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🌱 For younger babies, act it out during tummy time. Older babies might copy your sounds or movements."
msgstr "Okwezingane ezincane, lingisa ngesikhathi sokuhlala ngesisu. Izingane esezikhulile zona zingakopela imisindo neminyakazo."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👂 Talk to your baby as you play: “The cow says moo!” Pause and wait for their reaction, even a smile or babble."
msgstr "Khuluma nengane ngesikhathi nidlala: \"Inkomo ithi moo!\" Ima ulinde ukuthi bazokwenza njani, bazomamatheka noma babhibhidle."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "This gentle game builds language, movement, and bonding – one animal at a time! 💛"
msgstr "Lo mdlalo omnene usiza ukwakha ulimi, umnyakazo nokuxhumana - isilwane esisodwa ngesikhathi"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Adapted from Learning Through Play: https://learningthroughplay.com/let-s-play/act-like-an-animal"
msgstr "Iguqulwe ku Ukufunda ngokudlala: https://learningthroughplay.com/let-s-play/act-like-an-animal"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Rolling Ball Fun*"
msgstr "Ibhola eligingqikayo lenjabulo"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Time for a rolling game! 🔵"
msgstr "Isikhathi somdlalo wokugingqika"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👋 Sit facing your child and gently roll a soft ball (or something else round) back and forth between you. Say their name as you pass it: “Here it comes, Sisi!”"
msgstr "Hlala ubhekane nengane yakho, bese ugingqa ibhola elithambile kancane (noma yini eseduzane) uligingqele ngakuye naye aligingqele kuwena. Isho igama lakhe ngesikhathi ugingqela ngakuyena, \"Nali liza sisi\"!"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "💛 Cheer them on as they roll it back to you. You can even add a song or count the rolls out loud."
msgstr "Mujabulele ngesikhathi eligingqela ngakuwe. Ungaqala iculo noma ubale kakhulu ukuthi ligingqika kangakhi."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "This fun and easy game helps your toddler practise turn-taking, hand-eye coordination, and early social skills - all while enjoying playful connection 🎈"
msgstr "Lomdlalo omnandi usiza ingane yakho encane ukuphrakthiza ukushintsha, ukuhlangana kwezandla namehlo, ukuxhumana nabantu ngokushesha - konke lokhu ngesikhathi soxhumano olunokudlala"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Cup Stack Challenge*"
msgstr "Inselelo yokupakisha izinkomishi"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🍚 Grab some plastic cups or small containers and show your child how to stack them one by one. "
msgstr "Thatha izinkomishi zepulastikhi noma okungamakhonteyina amancane, bese ubonisa ingane yakho ukuthi wenza kanjani isitaki ngayinye ngayinye "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "⬆️ How high can you build your tower?"
msgstr "Ungawakha ube mude kangakanani umbhoshongo wakho?"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🎉 Knocking it down is just as fun - watch it fall, then build again!"
msgstr "Ukuwushaya phansi nakho kumnandi - ubukele uwa, bese uyawakha futhi!"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "This playful activity supports fine motor skills, concentration, and problem-solving - and your child will love seeing what happens each time they try 💡"
msgstr "Lomdlalo omnandi wesekwa ngamakhono, ukugxila nokusombulula izinkinga - kanti futhi ingane ingathanda ukubona ukuthi kwenzakalani njalo uma izamile"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Dance Mirror*"
msgstr "Isibuko Somdanso"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Let’s get moving and dancing together! ⭐"
msgstr "Masinyakaze futhi sidanse ndawonye"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👋 Turn on some music or sing a song, and start copying your child’s moves - if they clap, you clap! If they wiggle, you wiggle!"
msgstr "Dlala ingoma noma ucule ingoma, bese uqala ukopele umnyakazo wengane yakho - uma eshaya izandla nawe ushaya izandla! uma bezinyakazisa nawe uyazinyakazisa!"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👀 Then switch and see if they’ll follow your moves."
msgstr "Bese niyashintshana ubone ukuthi uzoyilandela iminyakazo yakho."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "This back-and-forth dance helps build confidence, strengthens your bond, and supports early communication skills."
msgstr "Lomdanso wokushintshana usiza ukwakha ukuzethemba, kuqinisa ubudlelwane benu, nokweseka amakhono okukhulumisana."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "It’s a joyful, silly way to connect through rhythm, music, and play 💚"
msgstr "Kuyajabulisa ukuxhumana ngokusebenzisa isigqi, umculo, nomdlalo"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Guess the Animal*"
msgstr "Qagela Isilwane"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Let’s guess the animal! 🧸"
msgstr "Masiqagele isilwane"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👂 Make a sound like a cow (“moo!”) or a dog (“woof!”) and ask your child, “Which animal is that?”"
msgstr "Yenza umsindo njengenkomo (\"moo!\") noma inja (\"woof!\") bese ubuza ingane yakho, \"Isiphi lesosilwane?\""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "⭐ You can point out animals you see, use toys, or just act it out yourself! "
msgstr "Ungakhomba izilwane ozibonayo, sebenzisa amathoyizi, noma ulingise "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👀 Then switch and ask them to make the noise - you’ll be surprised how many they know."
msgstr "Bese niyashintshana ucele yena enze umsindo - uzomangala ukubona ukuthi wazi eziningi kangakanani."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "This fun game builds memory, language skills, and listening - all through the power of play and imagination ✅"
msgstr "Lo mdlalo omnandi wakha inkumbulo, amakhono okukhuluma, nokulalela - konke lokhu kungamandla okudlala nomcabango"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Tap & Shake Band*"
msgstr "Ibhande lokuthepha futhi unyakazise"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Get ready to make some noise! 🔔"
msgstr "Zilungiselele ukwenza umsindo"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🍚 Gather safe household items - pots, plastic containers, spoons, or sealed bottles with rice or beans. "
msgstr "Qoqa izinto zasendlini eziphephile - amabhodwe, amakhonteyina aplastikhi, izipuni, amabhodlela avaliwe noma ubhontshisi "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👋Show your toddler how to tap, shake, and bang them together to create sounds."
msgstr "Khombisa ingane yakho encane ukuthi kwenziwa kanjani ukuthepha, ukushukuza nokushayanisa ndawonye ukwakha umsindo."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🎵 Now, make some music and form your own little band! You can sing along or try repeating rhythms together."
msgstr "Manje yenza umculo kulebhendi yakho encane! Ungacula nayo noma uzame ukuphindaphinda isigqi ndawonye."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "This activity builds motor skills, rhythm, and listening skills, and gives your toddler a chance to express themselves through sound and movement! ✨"
msgstr "Lo msebenzi wakha amakhono adingakalayo, isigqi, namakhono okulalela kunikeza ingane yakho encane ithuba lokuzichaza besebenzisa isigqi nomnyakazo"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Adapted from UNICEF Playbox: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ha943LSPtTY"
msgstr "Iguqulwe kwibhokisi lokudlala lakwa UNICEF: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ha943LSPtTY"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Where Did It Go*"
msgstr "Ishonephi"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Time for a little mystery! 🎁"
msgstr "Isikhathi semfihlakalo encane"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🧸 Hide a small toy under a soft cloth or behind your back and ask, “Where did it go?”"
msgstr "Fihla ithoyizi elincane ngaphansi kwendwangu noma ngemuva kwakho bese uyabuza, \"Lishonephi?\""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👀 Watch your child pull the cloth away or crawl over to investigate. "
msgstr "Bukela ingane yakho idonsa indwangu noma ikhasela ngalapho iyophenya "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔄 Take turns hiding and finding different objects together!"
msgstr "Shintshanani ngokufihla nokuthola izinto ezahlukene ndawonye!"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "This game helps your toddler develop memory, curiosity, and helps them understand that things still exist even when they’re out of sight! 💡"
msgstr "Lomdlalo usiza ingane yakho encane ukuthuthukisa inkumbulo, ilukuluku futhi ibasiza ukuqonda ukuthi izinto zisekhona noma zingekho phambi kwamehlo abo"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Lap Rhyme Bounce*"
msgstr "Ithanga Umlolozelo Gxuma"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🧸 Sit your baby gently on your lap and bounce them up and down while chanting a simple rhyme you remember from childhood."
msgstr "Hlalisa ingane yakho ethangeni lakho bese uyigxumisa phezulu naphansi ngalesoskhathi ube ucula umlolozelo owukhumbulayo usaseyingane."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "😃You can speed up or slow down the bounce for extra fun. Add facial expressions or tickles for extra giggles!"
msgstr "Ungakusheshisa noma ukwenze kancane ukumgxumisa ukwengeza ubumnandi. Fakela nokunyakazisa ubuso noma ukumkitaza ukuze agigitheke!"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "This rhythmic lap game builds bonding, listening, and body awareness - just like caregivers have done with little ones for generations 💙"
msgstr "Lomlolozelo wasethangeni wakha ubudlelwane, ukulalela nokuqonda umzimba - njengabazali benzile kwizingane zabo eminyakeni eminingi edlule"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Shadow Play*"
msgstr "Umdlalo wesithunzi"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Step into a world of imagination and light with this exciting activity! 🌙"
msgstr "Ngena emhlabeni womcabango nokhanya nomsebenzi wokuthakazelela"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "💡 In a darkened room, grab a light and shine it at your hand, casting fun shadows onto the wall. "
msgstr "Endlini emnyama, thatha ilambu likhanye esandleni sakho, ulokhu wenza isithunzi odongeni "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👋 Wave at your child and create silly shapes with your fingers - maybe a bunny, a bird, or whatever your imagination dreams up! "
msgstr "Valelisa enganeni wenze imifanekiso ehlekisayo ngeminwe yakho - mhlawumbe unogwaja, inyoni noma ikuphi okufika emcabangweni "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👀 Watch as their curiosity grows, and invite them to try waving their shadow hand back."
msgstr "Ukubuka ilukuluku lakhe likhula nokumumema ukuthi azame ukuvalelisa ngesandla sakhe."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔑 Encourage your little one to take a turn with the flashlight, giving them the thrill of seeing how light can create different shapes and movements on the wall. "
msgstr "Gqugquzela ingane yakho ukuthi nayo ithathe ilambu, abone ukuthi kumjabulisa kanjani ukubona ukuthi ilambu lingakwazi ukwakha imifanekiso neminyakazo odongeni "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🏁 Older children might want to join in the fun and make a shadow animal of their own!"
msgstr "Izingane ezindala zingafisa ukujoyina ukwenza isithunzi sesilwane ngokwabo!"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "This practical experience helps them understand cause and effect, and boosts their creativity and focus as they make shadows ✅"
msgstr "Ukwenza kubasiza ukuthi baqonde umsuka nomphumela, futhi ikhuphula ubuhlakani babo nokugxila uma benza isithunzi"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Adapted from Zero To Three: https://www.zerotothree.org/resource/play-activities-for-12-to-24-months/"
msgstr "Iguqulwe ku Ziro ukuya ku 3: https://www.zerotothree.org/resource/play-activities-for-12-to-24-months/"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Mini Obstacle Race*"
msgstr "Umjaho wezithiyo omncane"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Get ready to set up an exciting adventure right in your home! 🚩"
msgstr "Zilungiselele uhambo olujabulisayo khona ekhaya lakho"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔶 Using pillows, chairs, and blankets, create a fun and safe obstacle race for your toddler to explore. "
msgstr "Usebenzise imicamelo, izihlalo nezingubo zokulala, yenza ubumnandi nomjaho wezithiyo ophephile ukuze ingane yakho encane ihlole "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👋 The goal? For your little one to navigate the course by crawling, jumping, and climbing over, under, and through the obstacles."
msgstr "Injongo? Okwengane yakho ukuzitholela isifundo ngokukhasa, ukugxuma, nokugibela phezulu, ngaphansi nokudlula kwizithiyo."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "💡 As they tackle each challenge, they’ll be developing important gross motor skills like coordination, balance, and strength. "
msgstr "Njengoba bedlula kwizithiyo, bazithuthukisa ngokwenza iminyakazo emikhulu njengokuxhumanisa, ukubhalansa namandla "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "💛Not only will this activity get them moving, but it will also boost their confidence as they conquer each part of the race."
msgstr "Akusiwo wodwa umsebenzi obenza banyakaze, kodwa idlondlobalisa ukuzethemba uma belokhu benqoba zonke izithiyo zomjaho."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "It’s an easy, playful way to promote physical development while having a great time together! Let the obstacle adventure begin! 🎉"
msgstr "Kuyindlela elula, indlela enomdlalo ikhuthaza ukukhula komzimba ngesikhathi nichitha isikhathi esihle ndawonye! Makuqale ukwenza okungajwayelekile"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Adapted from Zero To Three: https://www.zerotothree.org/resource/10-olympian-inspired-activity-ideas-for-toddlers/"
msgstr "Iguqulwe ku Ziro ukuya kuThree: https://www.zerotothree.org/resource/10-olympian-inspired-activity-ideas-for-toddlers/"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Categorising and Organising*"
msgstr "*Ukuhlukanisa Nokuqoqa*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Help your child to learn by sorting objects and things! 🔵🔷"
msgstr "Siza ingane yakho ukufunda ngokuhlukanisa izinto! 🔵🔷"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "By grouping items like a bear as an animal or a mango as a fruit, they’ll start to understand how different things fit together. 🧸"
msgstr "Ukuqoqa izinto njengebhele isilwane noma umango njengesithelo, bazoqala ukuqonda uktuthi zixhumana kanjani"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "At home, find safe objects and let them sort them by colour, size, or type - plastic cups and plates are perfect for this! "
msgstr "Thola izinto eziphephile ekhaya ubayekele bahlunge ngokwemibala, ubukhulu noma uhlobo - izinkomishi namapuleti aplastikhi akulungele lokhu "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👀"
msgstr "Buka"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Want to make it more interesting? Try sorting pots and pans by size: Can they fit the small pans into the larger ones? ☕"
msgstr "Ufuna ukuyenza ibe nokuthakazelisa? Zama ukuhlunga amabhodwe namapani ngobukhulu: Bangakwazi ukufaka amancane kwamakhulu"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "If you are outside, name different kinds of vehicles on the street or things you see in nature like stones, sticks, trees and flowers. 🌷"
msgstr "Uma ungaphandle isho izinhlobo zezimoto ezisemgaqweninezinto eziyindalo ozibonayo njengamatshe, izinkuni, izihlahla nezimbali"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔄 You can play the categorising game anywhere! Just look around and ask your child to find things from the category you say!"
msgstr "🔄 Ningadlala lomdlalo wokuhlukanisa noma ikuphi! Buka eduzane bese utshela ingane yakho ukuthi ithole izinto kwisigaba osishoyo!"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Sorting and grouping builds thinking skills, memory, and early logic -helping your child make sense of the world around them through playful discovery 🌈 "
msgstr "Ukuhlunga kwakha ikhono lokucabaga, inkumbulo nokwazi ukucabanga ngokushesha okusiza ingane yakho ikwazi ukuqonda okwenzakalayo emhlabeni obazungezile ngokuthola ngokudlala "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Adapted from Brain Building Through Play by Harvard University: https://developingchild.harvard.edu/resources/brainbuildingthroughplay/"
msgstr "Iguqulwe ku Brain Building Through Play ngabase Havard University: https://developingchild.harvard.edu/resources/brainbuildingthroughplay/"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Shapes Everywhere!*"
msgstr "*Amasheyiphi Yonke Indawo!*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "📺 Squares, squares everywhere"
msgstr "📺 Izikwele, izikwele yonke indawo"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👀 Draw squares in the sand or dirt. Make some bigger and some smaller."
msgstr "👀 Dweba izikwele emhlabathini. Yenza ezinye zibe nkulu, ezinye zibe ncane."

#. type=text
#. Strings like @fields.xxx and @results.yyy should not be translated. 
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Tell @fields.child_nickname, “this is a square.” "
msgstr "Tshela u@fields.child_nickname, “lesi isikwele.” "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Ask your child to try to draw a square. Hold your child’s hand to help if this is hard. "
msgstr "Cela ingane yakho ukudweba isikwele. Bamba isandla sengane yakho ukuyisiza uma lokhu kunzima. "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Look for things around the home or outdoors that are the same shape."
msgstr "Funa izinto endlini noma ngaphandle ezinesheyiphi efanayo."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Now do the same with circles! 🔴"
msgstr "Manje yenza okufanayo ngezindlingilizi! 🔴"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Tell your child, “this is a square.” "
msgstr "Tshela umfana noma intombazane yakho, \"lesi isikwele.\" "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "This simple shape game builds early maths skills, observation, and coordination - right from the start! ✅"
msgstr "Lomumo womdlalo olula wakha ikhono lokubala ngokushesha, ukubona nokuxhumanisa - kusukela ekuqaleni"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Active Songs*"
msgstr "*Izingoma Zokwenza*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Young children love to move - and songs with actions make it even more fun! Singing gives your child cues for how and when to move 🎵"
msgstr "Izingane ezincane zithanda ukunyakaza - izingoma ezineminyakazo zenza kube mnandi kakhulu. Ukucula kusiza ingane yazi ukuthi kunyakazwa nini uma kuculwa"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Movement songs build listening skills, self-control, and rhythm - while helping your child learn to follow instructions!"
msgstr "Izingoma ezinomnyakazo zakha ikhono lokulalela, ukuzithiba nesigqi - ngesikhathi usiza ingane yakho ukulandela imiyalelo!"

#. type=text
#. Strings like @fields.xxx and @results.yyy should not be translated. 
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Sing songs to @fields.child_nickname or a group of children in which they have to:"
msgstr "Hlabelela ingoma ku@fields.child_nickname noma kwiqembu lezingane bona ekumele ba:"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "✅ Start and stop ❌"
msgstr "✅ Qale bese bayama ❌"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "⬇️ Slow down and speed up ⬆️"
msgstr "⬇️ Yenza kancane bese unyusa isipidi ⬆️"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Some song ideas:\r- “If you’re happy and you know it”\r- “Heads, shoulders, knees and toes”\r- “Freeze dance” (play or sing music and freeze when it stops!)\r- “Sleeping bunnies” (sleep, then hop!)"
msgstr "Eminye imiqondo ngomculo: - \"Uma uzazi ukuthi ujabule futhi uyakwazi lokho\" - \"Khanda, mahlombe, madolo nezinzwane\" nokudansa uma umculo uthula uyama unganyakazi\" - Onogwaja abalele ( lala, bese ugxuma gxume)"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Sing songs to your child or a group of children in which they have to:"
msgstr "Hlabelelela ingane yakho ingoma noma kwiqembu lezingane bona ekumele ba:"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Be the Narrator*"
msgstr "*Iba Ngumxoxi*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👀 Say what your child is doing while they are playing."
msgstr "Yisho okwenziwa yingane yakho ngesikhathi edlala."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👂 This will help them learn the words to describe their actions."
msgstr "👂 Lokhu kuzomusiza ukufunda amagama okuchaza izenzo zakhe."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "😃 You can do it in a simple way, or in a silly way like a sports commentator, a news presenter, or a game show host."
msgstr "😃 Ungakwenza lokhu ngendlela elula, noma esamahlaya njengomethuli wezemidlalo, umethuli wezindaba, noma umphathi wohlelo lomdlalo."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "💡 Ask questions like “What will you do next?” or “I see you want to put the ball in the jar. Is there another way to do that?”"
msgstr "💡 Buza imibuzo njengokuthi \"yini elandelayo ozoyenza?\" noma \"Ngiyabona ufuna ukufaka ibhola kujeke. Ikhona yini enye indlela yokwenza lokho?\""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Be an Artist!*"
msgstr "*Iba Usomaciko!*"

#. type=text
#. Strings like @fields.xxx and @results.yyy should not be translated. 
msgctxt "text"
msgid "📝 Give @fields.child_nickname some paper and a pen or pencil, or some different pens or pencils."
msgstr "📝 Nikeza u@fields.child_nickname iphepha nepeni noma ipensela, noma amapeni ahlukene namapensela."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "😃 Let your child draw whatever they want to!"
msgstr "😃 Dedela ingane yakho idwebe noma yini ayifunayo!"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👀 Ask questions about what they are drawing, the size of the thing they are drawing, and the colours they are using."
msgstr "👀 Buza imibuzo ngento ayidwebayo, usayizi bento ayidwebayo, nemibala ayisebenzisayo."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🏆 If possible, put your child’s picture up on the wall when they are finished. Give praise to your child!"
msgstr "🏆 Uma kwenzeka, beka isithombe sengane yakho odongeni uma eqeda. Income ingane yakho!"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "📝 Give your child some paper and a pen or pencil, or some different pens or pencils."
msgstr "📝 Nikeza umfana noma intombazane yakho iphepha nepeni noma ipensela, noma amapeni ahlukene namapensela."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "This open drawing time builds imagination, fine motor skills, and confidence - especially when you celebrate their creations! 🎉"
msgstr "Lesi sikhathi esivulelekile sokudweba sakha imicabango, amakhono okuzenzela izinto - kakhulu uma ujabulelela ubuhlakani babo"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Echo Songs*"
msgstr "Izingoma lapho kukhona oqalayo bese wonke umuntu elandela esho lokhu okushiwo oqalile"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "😃 Try a simple call-and-response chant with your child. You say a line, and they copy it back."
msgstr "Zama ingoma elula lapho kukhona oqalayo nengane yakho. Usho ulayini owodwa bese yena eyakopela ngokusho lokhu okushilo."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👂 For example:"
msgstr "👂 Ngokwesibonelo:"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "You: “Hello there!”"
msgstr "Wena: Sawubona!"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Child: “Hello there!”"
msgstr "Ingane: \"Sawubona!\""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "You: “How are you?”"
msgstr "Wena: \"Unjani?\""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Child: “How are you?”"
msgstr "Ingane: 'Unjani?\"?"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "💚 Use your own words and language."
msgstr "Sebenzisa amagama akho nolimi."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "These traditional-style echo songs build turn-taking, memory, and early conversation skills - all through playful singing 🎵"
msgstr "Lezingoma zasemandulo zokuqala omunye aphinde zakha ukushintshana, inkumbulo, nokuxhumana ngengxoxo ngokushesha - konke lokhu ngomdlalo wokuhlabelela"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Circle Clap and Dance*"
msgstr "Ukushaywa kwezandla nomdanso kwisikokela"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👋 Gather a few children (or just you and your little one) and form a small circle. "
msgstr "Qoqa izingane ezimbalwa( noma kube nguwe nengane yakho encane) nenze isikokela esincane "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🎵 Clap your hands in rhythm and sing a well-known local song like: “Shosholoza… ku lezontaba…”"
msgstr "Shaya izandla ngesigqi futhi ucule ingoma edumile endaweni elinjengaleli elithi \"Shosgoloza..... ku lezontaba\""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "⭐ As the song plays, take turns dancing into the centre of the circle or copying each other’s moves. Children can jump, spin, or stomp to the beat!"
msgstr "Ngesikhathi ingoma idlala, shintshanani ngokudansa esiphakathini sesikokela, ningakopela iminyakazo yabanye. Izingane zingagxuma, zipine noma zigidele ingoma!"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "This joyful game builds social confidence, movement skills, and musical rhythm - all while connecting to culture 💛"
msgstr "Lomdlalo omnandi wakha ukuzethemba, amakhono omnyakazo nesigqi somculo - konke kuxhumana namasiko"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*One-on-One Time*"
msgstr "*Isikhathi Ninobabili Nodwa*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "💚 Spending time just with your child and taking an interest in them can improve your relationship."
msgstr "Ukuchitha isikhathi nengane yakho yodwa nokuba nendaba nayo kungathuthukisa ubudlelwane benu.."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👀 When your child is playing alone or occupying themselves quietly, join them and show interest in what they are doing."
msgstr "Uma ingane yakho idlala yodwa iba matasa ngokuthula. mujoyine ukhombise ukuba nendaba kulokhu akwenzayo."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👂Ask questions about their activity, and listen to them."
msgstr "👂 Buza imibuzo ngomsebenzi awenzayo, bese uyalalela."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Let your child lead the activity, follow them to build their confidence and autonomy 😃."
msgstr "Dedela ingane yakho ihole umsebenzi. mulandele ukwakha ukuzethemba nokuzimela."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👀 Say what you see - describing everything and supporting your child’s actions."
msgstr "Isho okubonayo - chaza konke futhi weseke izenzo zengane yakho."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Be positive, praise your child, and enjoy spending this time with them 😃💚"
msgstr "Yiba sesimweni esihle, ncoma ingane yakho futhi ujabulele ukuchitha isikhathi naye"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "📖 Book sharing will help your child learn and is a fun, playful activity to spend quality time together."
msgstr "Ukwethula izincwadi kuzosiza ingane yakho ukufunda ngomdlalo ojabulisayo ukuchitha isikhathi esibalulekile ndawonye."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "⏰ Choose a time when you won’t be disturbed, and try to stop any distractions - e.g. turn off the TV and put away phones."
msgstr "⏰ Khetha isikhathi eningeke niphazamiseke ngaso, futhi uvimbe iziphazamiso - isib. cima iTV futhi ubeka amafoni."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "📖 If your child wants to choose a book, that’s fine, otherwise choose for them."
msgstr "📖 Uma ingane yakho ifuna ukukhetha incwadi, lokho kulungile, noma wena umukhethele."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Point at things, name and repeat words. Help them to learn more about what interests them in the book 👀 "
msgstr "Khomba izinto, isho amagama futhi uwaphinde. Msize ukufunda kakhulu ngezinto azinakayo encwadini 👀 "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Link things in the books to your child's life, and use words about emotions and talk about them! 😃"
msgstr "Qondanisa izinto encwadini nempilo yomntwana wakho, futhi usebenzise amagama emizwa bese ukhuluma ngawo! 😃"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Link things in the books to your child's life, and use words about emotions and talk about them! 😃."
msgstr "Qondanisa izinto encwadini nempilo yomntwana wakho, futhi usebenzise amagama emizwa bese ukhuluma ngawo! 😃."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Following Instructions*"
msgstr "*Ukulandela Imiyalelo*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "This will be useful in school, at home, and later in life!"
msgstr "Lokhu kuzosiza esikoleni, ekhaya, nasempilweni esikhathini esizayo!"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Start with just one instruction using an object in your home. For example “touch the red ball” 🔴"
msgstr "Qala ngomyalelo owodwa usebenzisa into esekhaya lakho. Isibonelo \"thinta ibhola elibomvu\" 🔴"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👀 Then say “I spy with my little eye, something beginning with *and then say the first letter of the word* which in this case is “b”"
msgstr "👀 Bese uthi \"Ngiyahlola ngehlo lami elincane, into eqala ngo *bese usho i-alfabethi yokuqala yegama* okungu \"b\" kulesisimo"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*What Letter is This?*"
msgstr "Lithini leligama?"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "📝 Write a letter on a piece of card or paper (e.g. “p”)"
msgstr "📝 Bhala i-alfabethi eyodwa kwibhodi noma ephepheni (isib. \"p\")"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔄 Try a new letter every day!"
msgstr "🔄 Zama i-igama elisha elilodwa ngosuku!"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Riddles and puzzles are a fun way to build thinking skills! 💡"
msgstr "Iziphicaphicana namaphazili ayindlela ejabulisayo yokwakha ikhono lokucabanga! 💡"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Do you remember any riddles from your childhood? If you can’t then make one up, they can be very simple! 😃"
msgstr "Uyazikhumbula iziphicaphicana zasebuntwaneni bakho? Uma uhluleka, yakha eyodwa, ingaba lula kakhulu! 😃"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Like “What can you see at night but not in the day” Answer: “The moon” 🌙"
msgstr "Njengokuthi \"Yini ongayibona ebusuku kodwa ayiveli emini\" Impendulo: \"Inyanga\" 🌙"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "You can have fun with riddles anywhere at any time - like traveling on a bus, walking to school or in a car 🚗"
msgstr "Ningazijabulisa ngeziphicaphicana noma inini nanoma ikuphi - njengokuhamba ngebhasi, ukuhamba ngezinyawo ukuya esikoleni noma phakathi kwemoto 🚗"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Make up a Story*"
msgstr "*Yakha Indaba*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🎂 Start your story with, “Once upon a time, there was a…” and use one of the words from the list in the first part. For example, “Once upon a time, there was a family who worked on a *banana* farm.”"
msgstr "🎂 Qala indaba yakho ngokuthi, \"Kwasukasukela, kwakukhona i...\" bese uqiniseka ukuthi usebenzisa elilodwa lamagama kuhlu lwakho. Isibonelo, \"Kwasukasukela, kwakukhona umndeni owawusebenza efamini *labhanana*.\""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔄 Take turns until you have used all the words and created a story. "
msgstr "🔄 Shintshisanani nize nisebenzise wonke amagama futhi seniyakhile indaba. "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Playing with Clothes*"
msgstr "*Ukudlala Ngezimpahla*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Playing with Vegetables*"
msgstr "*Ukudlala Ngemifino*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "😃 Remind me!"
msgstr "😃 Ngikhumbuze!"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Talk about your child’s experiences. Ask questions and wait for answers. Follow your child’s interests. "
msgstr "Khuluma ngezinto umfana noma intombazane yakho azibonile. Buza imibuzo futhi ulinde izimpendulo. Landela izinto umfana noma intombazane yakho azithokozelayo. "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Say: We are going to think of some things that are similar or different from what I tell you. So listen carefully!”"
msgstr "Ithi: \"Sizocabanga izinto ezifanayo noma ezihlukile kunalokho engizokusho kuwena. Lalelisisa!\""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Here is a tomato. Can you think of something else that is red like a tomato? 🍅"
msgstr "Nawu utamatisi. Ungacabanga enye into ebomvu njengotamatisi? 🍅"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Can you think of something else that is round like a tomato? ⚽"
msgstr "Ungacabanga enye into eyindingiliza njengotamatisi? ⚽"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Animals*"
msgstr "*Izilwane*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "What are all the animals we can think of that have feathers?"
msgstr "Iziphi zonke izilwane esingazicabanga ezinamaphiko?"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "What are all the animals we can think of that eat plants? 🌱"
msgstr "Iziphi zonke izilwane esingazicabanga ezidla izitshalo? 🌱"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "What are all the animals we can think of that lay eggs?"
msgstr "Iziphi zonke izilwane esingazicabanga izizalela amaqanda?"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "😃 Counting rabbits"
msgstr "😃 Ukubala onogwaja"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Active Counting*"
msgstr "*Ukubala Ngokwenza*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "1️⃣ Clap hands 1 time. 2️⃣ Clap hands 2 times."
msgstr "1️⃣ Shaya izandla kanye. 2️⃣ Shaya izandla kabili."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "1️⃣ Jump 1 time. 2️⃣ Jump 2 times."
msgstr "1️⃣ Gxuma kanye. 2️⃣ Gxuma kabili."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🏆 Can you clap twice, jump once, and hop three times?"
msgstr "🏆 Ungashaya izandla kabili, ugxume kanye, bese ugxuma kancane kathathu?"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "For example:"
msgstr "Isibonelo:"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Thinking Games*"
msgstr "*Imidlalo Yokucabanga*"

#. type=text
#. Strings like @fields.xxx and @results.yyy should not be translated. 
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Once @fields.child_nickname is familiar with the game, @fields.child_nickname will lead."
msgstr "Uma u@fields.child_nickname esewujwayele lo mdlalo, u@fields.child_nickname uzonihola."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Once your child is familiar with the game, your child will lead."
msgstr "Uma umfana noma intombazane yakho esewujwayele lo mdlalo, umfana noma intombazane yakho uzonihola."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Games with Pictures!*"
msgstr "*Imidlalo Enezithombe!*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Can you guess what it is?” 💚"
msgstr "Ungaqagela ukuthi yini?\" 💚"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*I'm a Writer!*"
msgstr "*Ngingumbhali!*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "📝 Have fun being creative with writing!"
msgstr "📝 Zijabulise ngokusungula ukubhala!"

#. type=text
#. Strings like @fields.xxx and @results.yyy should not be translated. 
msgctxt "text"
msgid "You and @fields.child_nickname can have fun writing with a pencil and paper, or with a stick and the sand!"
msgstr "Wena no@fields.child_nickname ningazijabulisa ngokubhala ngempensela nephepha, noma ngenduku nomhlabathi!"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Show them the simple things that you write - like shopping lists! Show them the words and each of the letters. Let them try to copy the words! 📖"
msgstr "Mutshengise izinto ezilula ozibhalayo - njengohlu lokuthenga! Mutshengise amagama nama-alfabethi akhona. Mudedele azame ukukopisha amagama! 📖"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "You and your child can have fun writing with a pencil and paper, or with a stick and the sand!"
msgstr "Wena nomntwana wakho ningazijabulisa ngokubhala ngempensela nephepha, noma ngenduku nomhlabathi!"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*A Friendly Chat*"
msgstr "*Inkulumo Yobungani*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Get Active*"
msgstr "*Yiba matasa*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "⏰ Even walking for 10 minutes a day is good for you. "
msgstr "⏰ Nokuchitha imizuzu ewu-10 ngosuku uhamba kukulungele. "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🏆 Together, think of ways to make it even more fun. Can you jog to a certain point? Take turns being the coach? Can there be a small, free reward, like getting to decide the next activity?"
msgstr "🏆 Ndawonye, cabangani izindlela zokwenza kubemnandi kakhulu. Ningagigjima kancane nize nifike endaweni ethize? Nishintshisane ngokuba ngumqeqeshi? Kungaba nomklomelo omncane, omahhala njengokukhetha into eningayenza elandelayo?"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🌈 Exercise becomes easier and more enjoyable the more you do it. "
msgstr "🌈 Ukuzivocavoca kubalula futhi kuba mnandi mawuqhubeka ukwenza. "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Pass the Ball*"
msgstr "*Dlulisa Ibhola*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Games are a great, fun way to spend time with your family! "
msgstr "Imidlalo ayindlela enhle, ejabulisanayo ukuchitha isikhathi nomndeni wakho! "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "3️⃣ This game is best with at least 3 people."
msgstr "3️⃣ Lo mdlalo ulungele abantu abawu-3 kuyela phezulu."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "⚽ Find a ball to play. If you cannot find a ball, choose an item you can safely throw around. For example, a bottle cap or a plastic cup."
msgstr "⚽ Thola ibhola lokudlala. Uma ungakwazi ukuthola ibhola, khetha into ephephile ongakwazi ukuyiphonsa. Isibonelo, isivalo sebhodlela noma inkomishi yeplastiki."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👋 Start throwing the ball in new directions (up, down, straight, curved, rolling on the ground) and with different forces (hard, soft, medium). You can bounce the ball, throw it in the air, and catch it a few times before passing it. "
msgstr "👋 Qala uphonse ibhola ngezindlela ezihlukile (phezulu, phansi, phambili, indlela egobile, ulirole phansi) futhi ngamandla ahlukile (ngokuqina, ngokuthamba, ngendlela ephakathi). Ungagxuma ibhola, uliphonse emoyeni, bese ulibamba kaningi ngaphambi kokulidlulisa. "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "✨ When everyone gets good at catching the ball, you can start moving around the room, still passing the ball. "
msgstr "✨ Uma bonke abantu sebelibamba kahle ibhola, ungaqala ukuhamba-hamba egumbini, usaqhubeka udlulisa ngokuphonsa ibhola. "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "⭐ Can you throw the ball under the leg? Behind the back? Over your head? Block a pass? Have fun with it!"
msgstr "⭐ Ungakwazi ukuphonsa ibhola ngaphansi komlenze? Ngemuva? Phezu kwekhanda lakho? Vimba iphasi? Zithokozise ngayo!"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Follow the Leader!*"
msgstr "*Landela Umholi!*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "😃 Other players line up behind the leader. The leader moves around in any way they like!"
msgstr "😃 Abanye abadlali bama emuva komholi. Umholi uyanyakaza nganoma iyiphi indlela ayithandayo!"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🏁 They can run, jump, crawl, walk on tiptoe, and any other way they want!"
msgstr "🏁 Bangagijima, bagxume, bakhase, banyonyobe, noma iyiphi enye indlela ayifunayo!"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👀 The other players must copy what the leader does, and the leader can change movements at any time."
msgstr "👀 Abanye abadlali kufanele balingise izenzo zomholi, futhi umholi angashintsha umnyakazo noma inini."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*What's New?*"
msgstr "*Yini Entsha?*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "For example: keeping a ball in the air with your foot, juggling, making soup, moonwalking, whistling, saying the alphabet backwards, learning all the countries in Africa. "
msgstr "Isibonelo: ukugcina ibhola emoyeni ngonyawo lwakho, ukuphonsa amabhola emoyeni uwabambe, ukwenza isobo, ukudansa, ukushaya ikhwela, ukusho i-alfabethi uqala ekugcineni, ukufunda zonke izizwe e-Afrika. "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔄 Take turns trying out the new skill. Make sure to praise each other and learn and play together!"
msgstr "🔄 Shintshisanani nizama ikhono elisha. Qiniseka ukuthi niyancomana futhi nifunde futhi nidlale ndwawonye!"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "😃 Once you have mastered the skill, choose another skill to learn together."
msgstr "😃 Uma usuphumelele kulelo khono, khetha elinye ikhono eningalifunda ndawonye."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*A friendly chat*"
msgstr "*Ingxoxo yobungane*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Talk to your teen about something that they are interested in! 😃"
msgstr "Khuluma nengane yakho ngokuthile enentshisekelo kukho! 😃"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "⚽ An easy way to start talking to your teen is to ask them about something they are interested in. For example, you could talk about sports, books, movies, friends, music, celebrities, or school."
msgstr "⚽ Indlela elula yokuqala ukukhuluma nengane yakho ukuyibuza ngokuthile enentshisekelo kukho. Isibonelo, ungakhuluma ngezemidlalo, izincwadi, amamuvi, abangani, umculo, osaziwayo, noma isikole."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👂 You may not find everything your teen shares to be interesting, but it’s important to show enthusiasm and an eagerness to learn."
msgstr "👂 Ungase ungatholi yonke into ingane yakho eyabelana ngayo ithandeka, kodwa kubalulekile ukukhombisa umdlandla kanye nokulangazelela ukufunda."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Create your own Recipe*"
msgstr "*Dala iresiphi yakho*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Let your teen come up with a new meal idea! "
msgstr "Vumela ingane yakho ukuthi ize nombono omusha wokudla! "

#. type=text
#. Strings like @fields.xxx and @results.yyy should not be translated. 
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🍚 Create a new dish with @fields.child_nickname using ingredients they love!"
msgstr "🍚 Dala isidlo esisha ngegama elithi @fields.child_nickname usebenzisa izithako abazithandayo!"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔵 Together, choose two ingredients, and ask your teen to prepare a meal using them. For example: chicken and spinach, tomatoes and rice, maize and pumpkin."
msgstr "🔵 Ndawonye, khetha izithako ezimbili, bese ucela osemusha wakho enze isidlo ngazo. Njengesibonelo: inkukhu nomfino, utamatisi nerayisi, impuphu nethanga."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "📝 If you enjoy the meal, make it something your family eats weekly and ask your teen to write it down for you, give the meal a name, and explain how to make it. "
msgstr "Uma ukuthokozela ukudla, kwenze kube into umndeni ozoyidla masonto onke futhi ungacela ingane yakho ikubhalele, kuqambe igama lokho kudla nokuthi uchaze ukuthi kwenziwa kanjani "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "✨ If your teen notices that you are learning from their cooking, it will boost their confidence!"
msgstr "✨ Uma ingane yakho iqaphela ukuthi ufunda ekuphekeni kwayo, kuzokhulisa ukuzethemba kwayo!"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🍚 Create a new dish with your teen using ingredients they love!"
msgstr "🍚 Dala isidlo esisha nengane yakho usebenzisa izithako abazithandayo!"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Reflect on the positive*"
msgstr "*Cabanga ngokuhle*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Spread Positivity! 🌈"
msgstr "Sabalalisa okuhle!🌈"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "💡 Together, take a minute to think about all the things you did today. "
msgstr "💡 Ndawonye, thatha iminithi lokucabanga ngazo zonke izinto ozenzile namuhla. "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "☀️ Take turns sharing one positive or fun thing that happened. This could be something small, like feeling good because you cleaned the house, or something big, like spending time with family and friends. "
msgstr "☀️ Shintshanani ngokwabelana ngento eyodwa eyakhayo noma ejabulisayo eyenzekile. Lokhu kungaba yinto encane, njengokuzizwa ujabule ngoba uhlanze indlu, noma into enkulu, njengokuchitha isikhathi nomndeni nabangane. "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "⏰ Try doing this every day - even more on the days it feels like you have not done anything special."
msgstr "⏰ Zama ukwenza lokhu nsuku zonke - nakakhulu ngezinsuku lapho kuzwakala sengathi awenzanga lutho olukhethekile."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*What’s new?*"
msgstr "*Yini entsha?*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Learning is fun! 🎓"
msgstr "Ukufunda kumnandi! 🎓"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "❓ Ask your teen to think of a new, fun skill you could learn together. "
msgstr "❓Cela osemusha wakho ukuthi acabange ikhono elisha, elimnandi eningalifunda ndawonye. "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔄 Take turns trying out the new skill.  Make sure to praise each other and learn and play together!"
msgstr "🔄 Shintshisanani nizama ikhono elisha. Qiniseka ukuthi niyancomana futhi nifunde futhi nidlale ndwawonye!"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "💛 Approach learning the skill in a kind and fun way, and do not judge your teen or yourself for your ability in the skill."
msgstr "💛 Sondela ukufunda ikhono ngendlela enomusa nejabulisayo, futhi ungahluleli ingane yakho noma wena ngokwakho ngekhono lakho kukhono."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Dance moves*"
msgstr "*Umdanso*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Let's get moving! 👋 Dancing is a great way to exercise, have fun, and bond with your teen at the same time! You both get to express yourselves in a fun, relaxed way.  🎵 "
msgstr "Masiqhubeke! 👋 Ukudansa kuyindlela enhle yokuzivocavoca, ukuzijabulisa, nobudlelwane nengane yakho ngesikhathi esisodwa! Nobabili nithola ukuveza imizwa yenu ngendlela ejabulisayo, ekhululekile. 🎵 "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "This game can be played in pairs or a group with everyone taking turns being the leader:"
msgstr "Lo mdlalo ungadlalwa nibabili noma eqenjini nabo bonke abantu bashintshisana ngokuba ngumholi:"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "📱 Let your teen choose a song they like and create a set of dance moves."
msgstr "📱 Vumela ingane yakho ikhethe ingoma eyithandayo, ihlanganise izinhlobonhlobo zemidanso."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👀 First person does a dance move and everyone else copies it."
msgstr "👀 Umuntu wokuqala wenza umdanso bese bonke abanye abantu bayayikopisha."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "☀️ Don’t worry about perfecting the dance moves, it’s all about having fun together!"
msgstr "☀️ Ningazikhathazi ngokwenza umdanso ube perfect, injongo ukuthi nizezenzele ubumnandi ndawonye!"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "💡 If you want to, you can perform your dance for the household!"
msgstr "💡 Uma ufuna, ungadlalela umndeni wakho umdanso!"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Dance Activity*"
msgstr "*Umsebenzi womdanso*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Try something new and learn a dance challenge with your teen! ✨ Have fun!"
msgstr "Zama into entsha futhi ufunde umqhudelwano wokudansa nosemusha wakho! ✨ Zijabulise!"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "⭐ Dancing is a great way to have fun together while being creative and moving your body!"
msgstr "⭐ Ukudansa indlela enhle yokuzijabulisa ndawonye nibe nidala futhi ninyakazisa umzimba!"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "📱 If your teen uses the app TikTok, suggest doing a dance challenge together."
msgstr "📱 Uma ngabe osemusha wakho esebenzisa uTikTok, faka isicelo sokuthi nenze umqhudelwano wokudansa ndawonye."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "😃 Ask your teen to choose their favourite dance and learn it with them."
msgstr "😃 Cela osemusha wakho ukuthi akhethe umdanso awuthandayo bese uyawufunda naye."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🎉 It’s okay if you can’t dance well, have fun and try not to take it too seriously! "
msgstr "🎉 Kulungile uma ungakwazi ukudansa kahle, zijabulise futhi uzame ukungayithatheli phezulu kakhulu! "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "💡 You do not have to post the video to learn the dance. You can keep it as a memory between you and your teen."
msgstr "💡 Awudingi ukuthumela ividiyo ukuze ufunde umdanso. Ungayigcina njengesikhumbuzo phakathi kwakho nengane yakho."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Check-in chat*"
msgstr "*Hlola imilayezo*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Actively checking in on one another helps to keep relationships healthy! ⭐"
msgstr "Ukuqhubeka nibhekana kuyasiza ukuthi nigcine ubudlelwano bunempilo! ⭐"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Ask each other questions: “What made you happy today?” 👂 “What was difficult today?” 👂 “How can I help you?” 👂"
msgstr "Buzanani imibuzo: \"Yini ekwenze wajabula namhlanje?\" 👂 \"Yini ebeyinzima namhlanje?\" 👂 \"Ngingakusiza kanjani? 👂"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "For this to help, your teen needs to feel safe while sharing things with you. Be open to their responses. 💚 Teens tend to be more honest when they trust that what they say will not be used against them later."
msgstr "Ukuze lokhu kusize, umntwana wakho osemusha udinga ukuzizwa ephephile ngenkathi ukutshela izinto. Zivule ukuzwa izimpendulo wakhe. 💚 Intsha ijwayele ukuba neqiniso kakhulu uma bethemba ukuthi abazokusho angeke kusentshiswe ukubalimaza kamuva."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Go easy on yourself if your teen does not want to share their problems with you. 💙 Often, teens are afraid to share as they are scared they will get in trouble. Getting upset with them won’t help - keep showing you love them and give them time! 🌷"
msgstr "Zikhululekele uma ingane yakho ingafuni ukwabelana nawe ngezinkinga zayo. 💙 Ngokuvamile, ingane iyesaba ukwabelana njengoba yesaba ukuthi izongena enkingeni. Ukucasuka ngabo ngeke kusize - qhubeka ubabonisa ukuthi uyabathanda futhi ubanike isikhathi! 🌷"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Express Yourself*"
msgstr "*Zibonakalise*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Dancing makes people happy!"
msgstr "Ukudansa kwenza abantu bajabule!"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🌈 This game can be played in pairs or as a group - stand facing each other or in a circle."
msgstr "🌈 Lo mdlalo ungadlalwa nibabili noma eqenjini - ima nibhekane noma endingilizini."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🎵 Together, choose a fun and upbeat song to play and a person to start the game by creating one dance move."
msgstr "🎵 Ndawonye, khethani ingoma emnandi enokujabula idlale bese umuntu aqale umdlalo ngokuthi adale umdanso owodwa."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👀 The person to their right must copy that dance move and add their own move to it."
msgstr "👀 Umuntu ongasesandleni sokudla kufanele akopishe lowo mdanso bese efaka umdanso wakhe."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "✨ Go around the circle, each person adding their own dance move to the full song."
msgstr "✨ Jikelezani endingilizini, umuntu nomuntu afake umdanso wakhe engomeni ephelele."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔄 The first one who forgets someone's dance moves or does it in the wrong order chooses the next song and starts the game again."
msgstr "🔄 Owokuqala okhohlwayo umdanso womunye umuntu noma oyenza nge-oda engalungile ukhetha ingoma elilandelayo bese uqala umdlalo futhi."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🎉 Try new dance moves with this game and have fun!"
msgstr "🎉 Zama ukunyakaza komdanso omusha ngalo mdlalo futhi ujabule!"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*2 Truths, 1 Lie*"
msgstr "*Amaqiniso amabili, amanga awodwa*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "This is a fun, quick game, and the point of it is to learn things about each other. Make your answers as interesting as possible! 🎨"
msgstr "Lona umdlalo ojabulisayo, osheshayo, futhi inhloso yawo wukufunda izinto ngomunye nomunye. Yenza izimpendulo zakho zibe mnandi ngangokunokwenzeka! 🎨"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "💡 Think of 3 facts about yourself. 2 must be true, 1 must be a lie. "
msgstr "Cabanga amaqiniso awu3 ngawe. Okubili kube iqiniso, okokodwa kube amanga "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔷 Here are some examples: I hate bananas, I have travelled to Kenya, my favourite subject in school was maths."
msgstr "🔷 Nazi izibonelo: Ngiyawuzonda ubhanana, ngake ngaya eKhenya, isifundo sami ebengisithanda esikolweni bekuyizibalo."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👀 Share the facts with your teen and ask them to guess which one is a lie. "
msgstr "👀 Yethula amaqiniso kumfana noma intombazane yakho futhi ubabuze baqagele ukuthi iyiphi engamanga. "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔄 Now ask them to do the same, and guess theirs."
msgstr "🔄 Manje bacele ukuthi benze okufanayo, bese uqagela okwabo."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Did you learn anything new about your teen, or did they learn anything new about you? 💛"
msgstr "Ingabe kukhona okusha okufundile mayelana nomntwana wakho, noma kukhona okusha umntwana akufundile ngawe? 💛"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Yes, No or Maybe*"
msgstr "*Yebo, Cha noma Mhlawumbe*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Are you tired of hearing your teen say yes, no, or maybe to all of your questions? Turn your chat into a game, and don’t allow one-word answers. 🎈"
msgstr "Ingabe ukhathele ukuzwa umfana noma intombazane yakho ethi yebo, cha, noma mhlawumbe kuyo yonke imibuzo yakho? Shintsha ingxoxo yakho ibe umdlalo, futhi ungamvumeli ukuthi aphendule ngegama elilodwa. 🎈"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔴 Teens are known to give one-word answers to avoid talking. "
msgstr "🔴 Intsha yaziwa ngokuphendula ngegama elilodwa ukugwema ukukhuluma. "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "💡 When you would like to really know how your teen is doing, you can turn your chat into a game. "
msgstr "💡 Ungafisa ukwazi nini ukuthi umfana noma intombazane yakho unjani, ungashintsha ingxoxo yenu ibe ngumdlalo. "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "⭐ Take turns asking each other questions. The only rule is that you cannot use one-word responses, such as Yes, No, Maybe, Fine, and Okay."
msgstr "⭐ Shintshisanani nibuzana imibuzo. Umthetho owodwa ukuthi anikwazi ukuphendula ngegama elilodwa, njengo Yebo, Cha, Mhlawumbe, Kahle, futhi Kulungile."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "⚽ You can ask about things your teen likes or what they did today. For example, how was your day? What are you excited for? Is there anything worrying you?"
msgstr "⚽ Ungabuza ngezinto umfana noma intombazane yakho azithandayo nokuthi wenzeni namhlanje.  isibonelo, belunjani usuku lwakho? Yini oyijabulele? Ngabe kukhona okukukhathazayo?"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔄 It is important to let your teen ask a question as well. Trust is built when your teen can see that you are also sharing your life with them, and not only trying to learn about their life."
msgstr "🔄 Kubalulekile ukuthi uvumele umfana noma intombazane yakho naye abuze umbuzo. Ukwethembana kwakheka lapho umfana noma intombazane yakho ebona ukuthi nawe wabelana nayo ngempilo yakho, awugcini ngokuzama ukufunda ngempilo yayo."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Movie World*"
msgstr "*Umhlaba Wefilimu*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Leaving the busy and stressful world behind can be good for our health. 🌱 Take a moment to escape with your teen by creating a superhero story together!"
msgstr "Ukushiya umhlaba ophithizelayo nokhathazanayo ngemuva kungaba yinto enhle ekuphileni kwethu. 🌱 Thatha umzuzu ube nomntwana wakho niqambe indaba engeqhawe ndawonye!"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🎈 Ask your teen to imagine that they are a superhero and what their superpowers would be. Flying? Time travel? Mind reading? Super Strength?"
msgstr "🎈 Cela umfana noma intombazane yakho wakho ukuthi acabange ukuthi uyiqhawe nokuthi amandla akhe angaba yini. Ukundiza? Ukubuyela emuva esikhathini? Ukufunda umqondo? Amandla Amakhulu?"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "✨ Ask them how they would use these superpowers, and why. "
msgstr "✨ Babuze ukuthi bangawasebenzisa kanjani amandla abo, futhi kungani. "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🌈 Help them give their superhero a name, an outfit, and a sidekick, and act it out. If your teen does not want to act, that is fine - talking about it is just as good!"
msgstr "Siza ukuthi baqambe iqhawe labo igama, izingubo zokugqoka, nomngani wakhe bese niyalingisa. Uma ingane yakho ingafuni ukulingisa, kulungile - ukukhuluma ngakho kwanele!"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👑 Now, let them make up a superhero for you. Play the part! You can ask questions, like who the villain would be, or how you became a superhero. "
msgstr "👑 Manje, badedele bakwakhele iqhawe. Lingisa! Ungabuza imibuzo, njengokuthi isitha kungaba ngubani, noma ube yiqhawe kanjani. "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "💡 Create a story - what happens to the characters? Is it an action story? Is it a thriller, space, sport, adventure, or romance?"
msgstr "💡 Dala indaba - kwenzekani kubalingiswa? Indaba eyokulwa? Indaba egijimisa igazi, umkhathi, ezimidlalo, indaba eyohambo, noma ezothando?"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "➡️ Next time you play this game, you could create a new story or superhero with your teen or continue the story you started together."
msgstr "➡️ Ngokuzayo uma udlala lo mdlalo, ungaqamba indaba entsha noma engeqhawe elinamandla nomntwana wakho noma niqhubeke nendaba eniyiqale ndawonye."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Exercise is a great way to spend time together and it is so good for your health. 🌱 Find a sport or exercise that both you and your teen want to do and try it out together! "
msgstr "Ukuzivocavoca indlela enhle yokuchitha isikhathi ndawonye futhi kulungele ukuphila kwenu. 🌱 Thola umdlalo noma indlela yokuzivocavoca wena nomntwana wakho bese niyazama ndawonye! "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "⚽ Together you can walk, run, play soccer, swim, dance, or do any other sport.."
msgstr "⚽ Ndawonye ningahamba, nigijime, nidlale ibhola, nibhukude, nidanse, noma nenze omunye umdlalo.."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔄 If you or your teen do not like the first exercise you pick, try a new exercise."
msgstr "🔄 Uma wena noma umfana noma intombazane yakho esanda kweva eshumini nambili ningawuthandi umsebenzi wokuqala owukhethayo, zama umsebenzi omusha."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Make up a story*"
msgstr "*Qamba inganekwane*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Creating stories together is a great way to learn the art of storytelling - and to build your teen’s creativity! 📖"
msgstr "Ukudala izindaba ndawonye indlela enhle yokufunda ubuciko bokuxoxa izindaba - futhi kwakha ikhono lokudala kumfana noma intombazane yakho wakho! 📖"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔟 With your teen, come up with 10 words to use. They can be any words you want! For example: banana, spaceship, fish, water, painting, wasp nest, cooking, wedding."
msgstr "🔟 Cabangani amagama ayi-10 ninomntwana wakho eningawasebenzisa. Kungaba inoma imaphi amagama eniwafunayo! Isibonelo: ubhanana, umkhumbi wasemkhathini, inhlanzi, amanzi, ukupenda, isidleke somnyovu, ukupheka, umshado."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🎂 Start your story with, “Once upon a time, there was a…” and make sure you use one of the words from the list in your sentence. For example, “Once upon a time, there was a family who worked on a *banana* farm.”"
msgstr "🎂 Qala indaba yakho ngokuthi, \"Kwasukasukela, kwakukhona i...\" bese uqiniseka ukuthi usebenzisa elilodwa lamagama kuhlu lwakho. Isibonelo, \"Kwasukasukela, kwakukhona umndeni owawusebenza efamini *labhanana*.\""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "📝 Let your teen make up the next sentence using another word from the list."
msgstr "📝 Vumela umfana noma intombazane yakho acabange umusho olandelayo ngokusebenzisa elinye igama kuhlu lwamagama eniwacabangile."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔄 Take turns until you have used as many words from the list as you can, or until you have finished your story. "
msgstr "🔄 Shintshisanani nize nisebenzise wonke amagama kuhlu eningawasebenzisa, noma nize niqede indaba yenu. "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔔 Be as creative as possible with your story and do not tell your teen what to say. It does not need to be a real story to be a good story!"
msgstr "🔔 Yakha kangangokho onakho ngale ndaba yakho futhi ungamtsheli umfana noma intombazane yakho ukuthi athini amagama owacabangile. Akudingeki ukuthi kuze kube indaba yangempela ukuze kube indaba enhle!"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🎁 Ask your teen what their favourite part of the story was, and tell them yours!"
msgstr "🎁 Buza umfana noma intombazane yakho ukuthi iyiphi ingxenye ayithanda kakhulu endabeni, bese uyitshela eyakho!"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Take A Pause with your teen*"
msgstr "*Thatha Ikhefu nomntwana wakho*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Take a pause with your teen. This helps them deal with stress in a healthy way!"
msgstr "Thatha ikhefu nomntwana wakho. Lokhu kubasiza ukubhekana nokukhathazeka ngendlela enempilo!"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "⏰ You could take a pause before dinner, after school, before school, or before bedtime."
msgstr "⏰ Ningathatha ikhefu ngaphambi kwesidlo sasebusuku, emva kwesikole, ngaphambi kwesikole, noma ngaphambi kwesikhathi sokulala."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👂 Sit down together and close your eyes. Listen to your breath as it goes in and out. Notice how you feel. "
msgstr "👂 Hlalani ndawonye bese nivala amehlo. Lalela umphefumulo kwakho uma uphuma ungena. Bheka ukuthi uzizwa kanjani. "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "⭐ Take 5 more deep breaths."
msgstr "⭐ Phefumula kakhulu kawu-5."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👀 When you are ready, open your eyes again. Do you feel any different? "
msgstr "👀 Uma usulungile, vala amehlo akho futhi. Uyawuzwa umehluko? "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "⏸ Ask your teen what it was like to take a pause. Listen and accept whatever they say about it."
msgstr "⏸ Buza umfana noma intombazane yakho ukuthi bekunjani ukuthatha ikhefu. Lalela futhi wamukele noma yini ayishoyo ngakho."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Name That Tune*"
msgstr "*Qamba leloculo*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Listening to music is a great way to lower your stress and have fun with your family. 💚"
msgstr "Ukulalela umculo indlela enhle yokwehlisa ukukhathazeka nokuzijabulisa nomndeni wakho. 💚"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "❓ Everyone else must guess the name and artist of the song."
msgstr "❓ Bonke abanye abantu kufanele baqagele igama nomculi wengoma."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🎉 The first one to guess it right becomes the next person to sing or play a song. "
msgstr "🎉 Owokuqala oqagela kahle kuba nguyena umuntu olandelayo oculayo noma odlala ingoma. "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔄 Keep going around until everyone has been able to play their favourite song and let the rest hear."
msgstr "🔄 Qhubekani nijikeleza kuze kube yilapho wonke umuntu esekwazi ukudlala ingoma yakhe eyintandokazi futhi aqiniseke ukuthi abanye bayezwa."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Pass the ball*"
msgstr "*Dlulisa ibhola*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "➡️ Start in a circle and pass the ball around. "
msgstr "➡️ Qala endlingilizini bese udlulisa ibhola. "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Make Housework Fun*"
msgstr "*Yenza Umsebenzi Wasendlini Ujabulise*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Turn your chores into games! 🏆 "
msgstr "Shintsha imisebenzi yasekhaya kube imidlalo! 🏆 "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "☀️ Making housework fun is a good way to teach your teen to be responsible and to rely on themselves. "
msgstr "☀️ Ukwenza umsebenzi wasendlini ujabulise indlela enhle yokufundisa umfana noma intombazane yakho ukuzimela. "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "📝 Together, make a list of all the chores that must be done in your home. "
msgstr "📝 Ndawonye, yenza uhlu lwayo yonke imisebenzi yasekhaya okufanele yenziwe. "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "💡 Make sure the tasks are fair and things your teen can do. For example, washing up, sweeping, mopping, making the beds, and laundry."
msgstr "💡 Qiniseka ukuthi imisebenzi ilungile futhi imisebenzi umfana noma intombazane yakho angayenza. Isibonelo, ukuwasha, ukushanela, ukukorobha, ukwendlula umbhede, nokuwasha izimpahla."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔄 Each week, let a different person in the family choose a chore first."
msgstr "🔄 Njalo ngesonto, dedela umuntu ohlukile emndenini ukuthi akhethe umsebenzi wasekhaya kuqala."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🎵 Play some music or turn on the radio. Music is a great way to make a boring task fun!"
msgstr "🎵 Dlala umculo noma ukhanyise umsakazo. Umculo indlela enhle ukwenza umsebenzi obhorayo ube mnandi!"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "✅ Tick off the tasks when they are done so you can see your progress as a family. You could offer small rewards as motivation to complete activities."
msgstr "✅ Thikha uma umsebenzi wenziwe ukuze nibone inthuthuko yenu njengomndeni. Ungabeka umklomelo omncane njengogqozi lokuqeda umsebenzi."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "📺 For example, you could let your teen watch more TV, spend more time with their friends, choose what they want for dinner, or have something sweet if they do their chores in a fair amount of time."
msgstr "📺 Isibonelo, ungavumela umfana noma intombazane yakho abukele iTV, achithe isikhathi nabangani bakhe, akhethe ukuthi kungaba isiphi isidlo sasebusuku, noma athole okunoshukela uma enza umsebenzi wakhe wasekhaya ngesikhathi esilungile"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "❓ If your child does not complete a chore, ask them why, and come up with a fair consequence together."
msgstr "❓ Uma umfana noma intombazane yakho engawuqedi umsebenzi othile, mbuze ukuthi kungani, bese niqhamuka nomphumela omuhle ndawonye."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*I’m Going on a Picnic and I Will Bring…*"
msgstr "*Ngiya kwipikiniki futhi Ngizophatha…*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Memory games are a fun way to strengthen our brains! "
msgstr "Imidlalo yenkumbulo indlela ejabulisayo yokuqinisa izingqondo zethu! "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🎂 Think of all the things you would have at your dream picnic. "
msgstr "🎂 Cabanga zonke izinto ongabanazo kwipikiniki yamaphupho akho. "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🎈 The first person says, “On Saturday, I am going to the park to have a picnic. To this picnic, I will bring...” and they say one thing they will bring to the picnic."
msgstr "🎈 Umuntu wokuqala uthi, \"NgoMqibelo, ngiya epaki ngiyoba nepikiniki. Kule pikiniki, ngizoletha...\" bese esho okukodwa azokuletha kupikiniki."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🍅 For example: a sandwich, a ball, a blanket, forks, cups, a dog, or coca cola."
msgstr "🍅 Isibonelo: isemishi, ibhola ingubo, izimfoloko, izinkomishi, inja, noma i-coca cola."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔔 The second person adds to the first person's list, but must start at the beginning: “On Saturday, I am going to the park to have a picnic. To this picnic, I will bring...” and say the item that the first person said AND then add their own item to the list."
msgstr "🔔 Umuntu wesibili wengeza kuhlu lomuntu wokuqala, kodwa kufanele aqale ekuqaleni: \"NgoMgqibelo, ngiya epaki ngiyoba nepikiniki. Kule pikiniki, ngizoletha...\" bese esho into eshiwo ngumuntu wokuqala BESE efaka nento yakhe lapho."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔄 Each time you add an item, you must say all previous items first - in the correct order!"
msgstr "🔄 Njalo mawufaka into, kefanele usho zonke izinto esezishiwo kuqala - zilandelana kahle!"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "⭐ Each person adds to the list, while remembering all the previous items. "
msgstr "⭐ Umuntu ngamunye uyafaka kuhlu, abe ekhumbula izinto esezishiwo ngaphambili. "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👀 If everyone has a turn, keep going and building your list. The first person to forget an item restarts the game!"
msgstr "👀 Uma wonke umuntu enethuba, qhubeka futhi wakhe uhlu lwakho. Umuntu wokuqala okhohlwa into ethile uqala kabusha umdlalo!"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*This is who I am*"
msgstr "*Yilokhu engiyikho*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Self-esteem is the way you value yourself, either in a positive or negative way. Helping your teen to have high self-esteem is a recipe for success! 🏆"
msgstr "Ukuzethemba yindlela ozazisa ngayo, ngendlela enhle noma embi. Ukusiza umtwana wakho umfana noma intombazane yakho ukuba azethembe kuyindlela yempumelelo! 🏆"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "⭐Share with your teen 3 things you like about yourself!"
msgstr "⭐ Yabelana numfana noma intombazane yakho wakho izinto ezi-3 ozithandayo ngawe!"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "3️⃣ Ask your teen to tell you 3 things they like about themselves. "
msgstr "3️⃣ Cela umtwana wakho umfana noma intombazane yakho ukuthi akutshele izinto ezintathu-3 azithandayo ngaye. "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "For example: I am great at treating others kindly. I am great at styling my hair. I am great at football. ⚽"
msgstr "Isibonelo: Ngimuhle ekuphatheni abantu ngomusa. Ngimuhle ukwenzeni izinwele zami. Ngimuhle ekudlaleni kwebhola. ⚽"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "If your teen does not feel comfortable sharing these, ask them to write them down. 📝"
msgstr "Uma umfana noma intombazane yakho ingazizwa ikhululekile ukwabelana ngalokhu, yicele ukuthi ikubhale phansi. 📝"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Things I like about others and me*"
msgstr "*Izinto engizithanda ngami nangabanye*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "☀️Ask your teen to share 3 things they like about a friend or someone they admire, like a celebrity."
msgstr "☀️ Mucele umtwana wakho umfana noma intombazane yakho ukuthi akutsele izinto ezintathu-3 azithandayo ngomngani noma umuntu amazisayo, njengosaziwayo."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "❓ Ask them if they share any of these qualities, too."
msgstr "❓ Babuze uma benazo nabo lezimfanelo ezifanayo."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "💙 You can do the same: share with your teen the qualities you like about yourself or about someone you admire - and what you like about your teen!"
msgstr "💙 Ungenza okufanayo: yabelana nomntwana wakho ngezimfanelo ozithandayo ngawe noma ngothile omthandayo - nalokho okuthandayo ngengane yakho!"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Make a family wish list*"
msgstr "*Yenza uhlu lwezifiso zomndeni*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Wish lists are a great way to set, plan and keep track of your goals and dreams. 🌷 "
msgstr "Uhlu lwezifiso indlela enhle yokuhlela nokulandelela izifiso namaphupho akho. 🌷 "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "📝 To start your wish list, gather your family together and grab pens and paper. "
msgstr "📝 Ukuqala uhlu lwakho lwezifiso, hlanganisa umndeni wakho ndawonye bese nithola amapeni namaphepha. "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🚲 Allow each family member to write a list of goals and experiences they want to achieve this year."
msgstr "🚲 Vumela amalunga omndeni abhale uhlu lwezifiso kanye nezinto abafisa zifezeke kulo nyaka."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🎂 For example: exercise daily, read 1 book a month, make a new friend, learn to bake a cake, learn to juggle, or go watch the local soccer team play. "
msgstr "🎂 Isibonelo: ukuzivocavoca nsuku zonke, funda incwadi eyodwa ngenyanga, ukwenza umngani omusha, funda ukubhaka ikhekhe, funda ukuphonsa amabhola emoyeni uwabambe, noma hamba uyobheka iqembu lebhola lasendaweni lidlala. "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔔 Once you have finished, put the list up where everyone can see it daily."
msgstr "🔔 Uma seniqedile, beka uhlu lapho bonke abantu bazolubona khona nsuku zonke."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🎉 As members of the family reach their goals, tick them off the list and celebrate each goal reached. "
msgstr "🎉 Njengoba amalunga omndeni afeza izifiso zabo, thikha kuhlu bese nibungaza isifiso esifezekile. "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "❓ As the year goes on, there might be some items some of you have not achieved. Talk to your family about whether you still want to reach this goal or whether the goal has changed. "
msgstr "❓ Njengoba unyaka uqhubeka, kungenzeka ezinye izinto, abanye benu azifezekanga. Khuluma nomndeni wakho mayelana nokuthi usafuna ukufeza lesi sifiso noma isifiso sesishintshile. "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔑 If you still want to achieve the goal, discuss with your family what you need to do to tick the goal off your wish list."
msgstr "🔑 Uma usafuna ukufeza umgomo, xoxisana nomndeni wakho ngalokho okudingeka ukwenze ukuze ukhathule umgomo ohlwini lwakho lwezifiso."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Weekly Goal Setting*"
msgstr "*Ukulungiselelwa Komgomo Wamasonto onke*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Let’s set some goals ⭐"
msgstr "Asibeke imigomo ethile ⭐"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "⏰ It can be helpful to set smaller weekly goals that are easier to reach. This helps us reach our larger goals over time."
msgstr "⏰ Kungaba usizo ukuzibekela imigomo emincane yamasonto onke okulula ukuyifinyelela. Lokhu kusisiza ukuthi sifinyelele imigomo yethu emikhulu ngokuhamba kwesikhathi."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "💡Ask your teen for one goal that they would like to achieve this week. "
msgstr "💡Buza umfana noma intombazane yakho umgomo owodwa engathanda ukuwufinyelela kuleli sonto. "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔄 Make sure this goal is *specific* and  *achievable* to reach in 1 week."
msgstr "🔄 Qiniseka ukuthi lo mgomo *uqondile* futhi *uyafinyeleleka* ukuze uwufinyelele evikini elilodwa."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "💚 You can also share your own weekly goal with your teen and support each other so you can both achieve your goals."
msgstr "💚 Ungakwazi futhi ukwabelana ngomgomo wakho weviki nomntwana wakho futhi nisekelane ukuze nobabili nifinyelele imigomo yenu."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🎉 Make sure to praise and celebrate your teen for their hard work towards reaching their goal."
msgstr "🎉 Qiniseka ukuthi uyayincoma futhi uyibungaze umfana noma intombazane yakho ngomsebenzi wayo onzima ukuze ifinyelele umgomo wayo."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔔 If your teen does not reach their goal, that is okay. Discuss with your teen the steps they still need to take or how they could reach it a different way."
msgstr "🔔 Uma umtwana wakho umfana noma intombazane yakho engafinyeleli kumgomo wakhe, kulungile. Xoxisana nomtwana wakho umfana noma intombazane yakho ngezinyathelo asadinga ukuzithatha noma ukuthi angafinyelela kanjani kuzo ngendlela ehlukile."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Think Big, Think Small*"
msgstr "*Cabanga kakhulu, Cabanga kancane*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Working towards big goals can be hard! Here is a way you can help your teen set new goals for the things they want to achieve. 👑"
msgstr "Ukusebenzela izifiso ezinkulu kungaba nzima! Nansi indlela ongasiza ngayo umfana noma intombazane yakho wakho ukusetha amagoli ezintsha abafuna ukuzifeza. 👑"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👑 Ask your teen to come up with three things that they are good at, and discuss what they did to become so good at them. For example: keeping their room neat, helping your family with housework, or playing a sport."
msgstr "👑 Cela umfana noma intombazane yakho wakho ukuthi asho izinto ezintathu azenza kahle, futhi nikhulume ngokuthi benzeni ukuze bazenze kahle. Isibonelo: ukugcina ikamelo labo niqoqekile, ukusiza umndeni wakho ngomsebenzi wasendlini, noma ukudlala ezemidlalo."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🏆 Next, ask your teen what they wish they were good at. "
msgstr "🏆 Okulandelayo, buza umfana noma intombazane yakho wakho ukuthi ufisa ukuthi ebemuhle ekwenzeni ini. "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔑 Remind them that it took work and practice to become good at the skills they have. They will have to do the same for any new goal."
msgstr "🔑 Bakhumbuze ukuthi kwathatha umsebenzi nokuzijwayeza ukuze abemuhle kulamakhono anawo. Kufanele benze okufanayo kunoma isiphi isifiso esisha."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "⏰ Help your teen break down their goal and set up smaller goals they need to achieve to reach their greater goal."
msgstr "Siza ingane yakho ukucozulula umgomo wakhe futhi azinqumele imigomo emincane abayidingayo ukufeza nokufinyelela kumgomo omkhulu."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "📝 It is much easier to achieve a goal if you write it down! This way, you can be reminded of it as you work towards it."
msgstr "📝 Kulula kakhulu ukufeza isifiso uma usibhala phansi! Ngale ndlela, ungakhunjuzwa ngaso njengoba usebenzela ukufika kuso."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "☀️ For example, if the goal is to be good at football, small weekly goals could be to go to football practice 2 times per week, run at least 1 km 5 times per week, and learn about the sport from other football players in the community or from books or videos they find. "
msgstr "☀️ Isibonelo, uma isifiso ukuba muhle ebholeni, izifiso ezincane zesonto kungaba ukuya ebholeni kabili ngesonto, ugijime okungenani ikhilomitha kawu-5 ngesonto, futhi ufunde ngebhola kwabanye abadlali bebhola emphakathini noma ezincwadini noma kumavidiyo abawatholayo. "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "✅ It is important to write down these smaller goals and let your teen tick off each task as they do them each week. Seeing themselves reach smaller goals will keep them motivated to achieve the big goal!"
msgstr "✅ Kubalulekile ukubhala phansi le migomo emincane futhi uvumele umfana noma intombazane yakho ukuthi iphawule umsebenzi ngamunye njengoba iwenza isonto ngalinye. Ukuzibona befinyelela imigomo emincane kuzobagcina benogqozi lokufinyelela umgomo omkhulu!"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Role Playing*"
msgstr "*Ukudlala indima*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Let’s start acting! ⭐"
msgstr "Masiqale ukulingisa! ⭐"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "✨ Ask your teen if they want to role play with you. You can also suggest a topic. For example, asking someone on a date, saying no to drugs/alcohol/sexting, dealing with a bully, getting a bad grade, or dealing with gossip."
msgstr "✨ Buza umtwana wakho umfana noma intombazane yakho ukuthi uyafuna yini ukudlala indima nawe. Ungafaka isicelo sesihloko. Isibonelo, ukucela othile ukuzikhipha naye, ukungqaba izidakamizwa/utshwala/imiyalezo yocansi, ukubhekana nohlukumeza abanye, ukuthola amamaki amabi, noma ukubhekana nenhlebo."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🌙 Your teen could play the role of a friend asking you to drink at a party. You could role play an underage teen who does not want to drink. Encourage your teen to be silly and really get into character with them. "
msgstr "🌙umfana noma intombazane yakho wakho angalingisa indima yomngani okucela ukuthi uphuze ephathini. Wena ungalingisa indima yomntwana umfana noma intombazane yakho ongafuni ukuphuza. Gqugquzela umfana noma intombazane yakho umfana noma intombazane yakho ukuthi abe isiphukuphuku futhi angeni esimeni ngokuphelele. "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "⏯️ After you act out the scene, it is important to talk to your teen about the actions that you role played. You can act out this scenario as many times as you like!"
msgstr "⏯️ Ngemva kokulingisa indawo, kubalulekile ukukhuluma nomntwana wakho mayelana nezenzo ozililile. Ungalingisa lesi simo izikhathi eziningi ngokuthanda kwakho!"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Traffic Lights*"
msgstr "* Izibani Zomgwaqo*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "A group activity is a great way to bond with others! 💛 "
msgstr "Umsebenzi weqembu uyindlela enhle yokuhlangana nabanye! 💛 "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "💡 Choose one person to turn and face a wall. This will be the traffic officer. "
msgstr "💡 Khetha umuntu oyedwa ukuthi ajike abheke udonga. Lona kuzoba iphoyisa lomgwaqo. "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🏁 Everyone else will begin the game at the other side of the room, or if you are outside, at a starting line. Set a long distance between the traffic officer and the players."
msgstr "Wonke umuntu uzoqala umdlalo engakolunye uhlangothi endlini, uma kwenzeka ungaphandle kumugqa wokuqala. Setha ibanga elikhulu phakathi kwephoyisa lomgwaqo nabadlali."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "💚 The game begins when the officer shouts “Green”, and everyone can start moving towards the traffic officer at any speed they choose. "
msgstr "💚 Umdlalo uqala uma iphoyosa limemeza \"Umbala oluhlaza\", bese bonke abantu bangaqala ukusondela ephoyiseni lomgwaqo nganoma isiphi isivinini abasikhethayo. "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔴 The officer can shout “Red!” at any time, without looking behind them. When they shout this, everyone must stop and freeze! "
msgstr "🔴 Iphoyisa lingamemeza lithi \"Umbala obomvu!\" nganoma isiphi isikhathi, ngaphandle kokubheka ngemuva. Uma limemeza lokhu, wonke umuntu kufanele ame futhi anganyakazi! "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "⏸ The officer turns around to see if everyone is frozen. If they see anyone moving, they have to send them back to the start line."
msgstr "⏸ Iphoyisa liyaphenduka ukubona ukuthi wonke umuntu akanyakazi. Uma ebona umuntu onyakazayo, kufanele amubuyisele emuva ayoqala phansi."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🏆 The winner is the first person to get to the officer without being sent back to the start."
msgstr "🏆 Umanqoba umuntu owokuqala ofika ephoyiseni ngaphandle kokubuyiselwa ekuqaleni."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👑 The winner then becomes the traffic officer and you can play another round!"
msgstr "👑 Owinile ube eseba iphoyisa lomgwaqo futhi ungadlala omunye umzuliswano!"

